#Hello!

I am a scientist and software developer. I have a wide variety of interests including software development, proteomic data analysis, and machine learning. Thanks for stopping by!

##Check out my latest project in label-free quantitative (LFQ) proteomic analysis:
* [Morpheus Spectral Counter or MSpC](http://dcgemperline.github.io/Morpheus_SpC/)
